- Light content sections (#F4F9F6) = breathing room and legibility
- Gold (#C89749) divider lines between major page sections
- All number/score displays use JetBrains Mono — always
- Subtle Framer Motion fade-up on scroll for every section
- Mobile-first always — design for 375px, enhance upward

